<p>I recommend The Sense of Style: The Thinking Personâ€™s Guide to Writing in the 21st Century by Stephen Pinker; Politics and the English Language by George Orwell, and Spunk &amp; Bite: A Writerâ€™s Guide to Bold by Arthur Plotnik. Read the last one last, as itâ€™s about how to intelligently break the â€œrules,â€ and itâ€™s worth knowing what they are first.</p>

